zsigmond worked with brian de palma on obsession , blow out , the bonfire of the vanities , and the black dahlia , with michael cimino on the deer hunter and heaven 's gate , with richard donner on maverick and assassins , with kevin smith on jersey girl , with george miller on the witches of eastwick , with mark rydell on cinderella liberty , the rose , the river , and intersection , and with woody allen on melinda and melinda , cassandra 's dream , and you will meet a tall dark stranger .

